spanGrp.span: ‘By the Ujarraz road there is uh…
Ujarras ñala tsõ/ ñala wa ra/ je tsõ (_) tsõ estee
those are trees called guancaste; there are many of them.
by Wilberth’s there are many thermal waters.
Wilbert ska (hm) estee (hm) agua (r) terma (r) agua termales tsõ tã'ĩ
and bathe there uh… in the hot water.
jugö jega estee diglö bal wa
Here in Buenos Aires, by this road uh…
Ji Buenos_Aires wa ra je ñala wa ra estee
there is a lot of pineapple uh… many ripe pinapples.
piña tsõ tã'ĩ estee bishkö li tsõ tã'ĩ
There are lots of people around here.’
Tã'ĩ tã'ĩ pe tsõ ji wa
